<HEADLINE>
<P>
OBITUARIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Aguilar, Sophia, 77, of Sun Valley, homemaker. San Fernando Mortuary, San 
Fernando.  
</P>
<P>
