 Brett Butler will miss tonight's game to be with his mother, Betty, who is 
undergoing surgery early Thursday morning in Chicago. Butler, who will travel 
to Chicago today, plans to join the team in Atlanta Thursday evening in time 
for the three-game series against the Braves, which begins Friday. MARYANN 
HUDSON 
