<P>
 Ventura fire officials are investigating the cause of a suspicious brush fire 
that broke out Tuesday north of Hillcrest Drive, near Catalina Street. 
</P>
<P>
 Ventura Battalion Chief Bill Rigg said investigators could not find remnants 
of a cigarette or any other accidental cause of the blaze that consumed about 
