<DOCNO> LA060194-0155 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 047245 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 1, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 6; National Desk 
</P>
